Selected soil description: The Botella series consists of very deep, well drained soils that formed in alluvial material from sedimentary rocks. Botella soils are in valley bottoms and on alluvial fans and have slopes of 0 to 15 percent. The mean annual precipitation is about 457 mm (18 inches) and the mean annual air temperature is about 14 degrees C (58 degrees F).
